result.adr_address: 98 Wellington St, Central, Hong Kong
result.name: Tsim Chai Kee Noodle Shop

reviews.text: Walked in on a whim based on the crowd. Did not disappoint. Got the noodle with the 3 meats and it came out fast. Add the chili on the table if you want it spicy. So good!

Standard noodle place. Very good value for money, but don't go here if you are following any particular diet or are looking to shop organic. Quick service but it's cash (or octopus) only when it comes to payment. Still, one of the better places to get a quick, cheap fill in Central around LKF.

Taste of childhood.. the tiny little stall in Prince Edward ages ago. Now elegantly presented in Central, with bargain price tag but good quality. The won ton was so meaty with king prawn inside.. soup was yum yum. Veg was nice full of bean curd sauce. Highly recommended for a quick bite in Central.

Speedy and friendly service. English and Japanese menus are available. The noodles are offered in both soup and dry versions but it's not stated in the English menu. Just request it with the server though the dry version cost a little more than the soup version. Will definitely return the next time I visit Hong Kong.

Tried several several famous wanton shops in Hong Kong. This is still my favourite. Their noodle texture and taste is springy and great. Even their soup is superb. I foresee myself going back whenever I’m back in Hong Kong in the future.

result.adr_address: 香港中環威靈頓街98號
result.name: 沾仔記

reviews.text: 雲吞真的好好吃喔😋

토핑을 2-3가지까지 선택할 수 있는데,
저라면 새우만 선택하겠습니다. 
가득찬 새우살에 육즙이 굉장해요.
면은 독특하게 쫄깃한데, 육수와 따로노는 느낌이 있어서 제 입맛에는 안맞았어요.
Walked in on a whim based on the crowd. Did not disappoint. Got the noodle with the 3 meats and it came out fast. Add the chili on the table if you want it spicy. So good!

1月に観光したときの写真です。

香港島にある、中環にある沾仔記（カントン語でティムチャイキーと読みます）へ、香港人の彼氏に連れて行ってもらいましたー！！！

平日のお昼時、仕事途中のひとたちも食べにきていました。観光客の方が行列のなかで少ないくらい大人気ー！！

10人以上並んでいましたが、回転が速いためにすぐに呼ばれました。

海老のワンタン麺にしましたー！！

出てくるのもとても早くて、麺がゴムみたいでした笑笑

ワンタンがめちゃくちゃ美味しかったー！

温かくて、体もとても暑くなり、美容にも良さそうですねー！！

食べてよかったー！

どうもありがとうございます。
ごちそうさま。
저렴한 완탕 누들집. 저렴한 가격에 적당한 양과 맛. 처음에는 완탕누들로 시작해보자. 면을 고를 수 있고  둘 이상갔다면 야채볶음을 추가해서 먹으면 좋다.
